OL,3,CDame Tracey Emin fronts TfL's non-
OL,4,Cvisible disabilities campaign
OL,6,FDame Tracey Emin is urging Londoners
OL,7,Fto offer up their seats to help people
OL,8,Fwith non-visible disabilities in a new
OL,9,FLondon Tube campaign.
OL,11,FThe artist, voicing the travel
OL,12,Fannouncements for TfL's annual
OL,13,FPriority Seating Week, now lives with
OL,14,Fa stoma bag after undergoing life-
OL,15,Fsaving surgery following a bladder
OL,16,Fcancer diagnosis in 2020.
OL,18,FThe 62-year-old, hoping to raise
OL,19,Fawareness, says she understands the
OL,20,Fimpact that "standing on a train" can
OL,21,Fhave on someone with a impairment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
