OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778677871
OL,3,CDame Tracey Emin fronts TfL's non-
OL,4,Cvisible disabilities campaign
OL,6,FShe said: "Any one of us can have a
OL,7,Fhealth condition or disability, and
OL,8,Fbecause many of these don't have
OL,9,Foutward cues, that might mean people
OL,10,Fmiss out on things that would really
OL,11,Fhelp them, like getting a seat on
OL,12,Fpublic transport.
OL,14,F"If you're out and about in London,
OL,15,Fplease do offer your seat if you don't
OL,16,Fneed it yourself ` you never know what
OL,17,Fa difference you could make."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
