PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778677871
OL,3,CDame Tracey Emin fronts TfL's non-
OL,4,Cvisible disabilities campaign
OL,6,FHer announcement will be played across
OL,7,Ften central London Underground
OL,8,Fstations, including Bank, Canary
OL,9,FWharf, Liverpool Street, as well as
OL,10,Fbus stations until 17 May 2026.
OL,12,FGiovanni Cinque, Campaigns Manager at
OL,13,FColostomy UK, said difficulties on
OL,14,Fpublic transport are not always
OL,15,Fvisible but can be "distressing", and
OL,16,F"a small act of kindness like offering
OL,17,Fa seat can have a significant impact".
OL,26,@wD@TOUwD@`O]xD@AOUyD@eO]
